# Asset Management - Git Ignore for Large Files
# Files >500KB should be compressed or hosted externally

# Large blog images (>500KB) - Consider compression
images/blog/comms/rosenslides/*.png
images/blog/comms/blog/robot-*.png

# Temporary and working files
*.tmp
*.temp
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Large generated files
diagrams/generated/*.png
documents/exports/*.pdf
